look like your mom.

18
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,520
My mom?

19
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,840
Do you know her?

20
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:49,600
Do you have a dragon scale on you?

21
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:53,800
How...

22
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,680
