32
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,240
and the scale would respond.

33
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,240
It's you.

34
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,800
It's you that have been protecting me in secret

35
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:32,880
and keeping me safe.

36
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,120
So...

37
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:37,760
So...

38
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,680
Who on earth are you?

39
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,160
I'm your father.

40
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,000
What?

41
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,280
Fath...

42
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,520
No.

43
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,640
No.

44
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,560
Impossible.

45
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:01,800
Nobody has ever told me about that.

46
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,160
You and my mom...

47
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,000
You've never...

48
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,680
Heng,

49
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,240
in those years,

50
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:13,960
unable to bear Demon Lord Chi 's torture anymore,

51
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:17,240
your mom ran away from the demons and then met me.

52
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:21,440
We concealed our true names and came to the south desert.

53
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,800
Then you were born.

54
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,360
Are...

55
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,920
Are you really...

56
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,400
...my father?

57
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:48,120
Your Majesty.

58
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:59,360
I'm so glad to see you again before I die.

59
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,120
Don't do that.

60
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,000
Why are you so badly injured?

61
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,560
It's okay.

62
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,200
Your Majesty, don't worry.

63
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,040
Your Majesty,

64
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,960
she's my daughter

65
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,000
Ji Heng.

66
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,280
You insisted on staying here

67
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,120
just because of her, right?

68
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,200
It's all my fault.

69
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,400
I wanted to save Min Su,

70
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,480
so he was severely injured.

71
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,640
He was injured to save me.

72
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:43,910
Your Majesty,

73
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,400
please save him.

74
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,480
You can save him, right?

75
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,150
It's too late.

76
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,600
No.

77
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,600
No.

78
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,160
It's not true.

79
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:57,920
Your Majesty,

80
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:02,400
can you do me a favor?

81
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,000
Go ahead.

82
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,080
Ji Heng

83
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:10,600
is poisoned with Qiushui Cold Toxin.

84
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,800
and I can't take care of her anymore.

85
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,920
Can you take care of her

86
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:22,600
and keep her safe?

87
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,880
Trust me. I will take care of her

88
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,640
and try to detoxify the poison.

89
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:27,880
No.

90
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,480
I'll hate you.

91
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,320
Stay.

92
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,680
I'll hate you if you leave.

93
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,760
I'll hate you all my life.

94
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,720
No.

95
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:36,720
No.

96
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:37,640
Dad.

97
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:38,920
Dad.

98
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,040
Dad.

99
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,320
Dad.

100
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,960
Dad.

101
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,560
Where are you from, little fox?

102
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:57,880
Where are you from?

103
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,200
Jiu.

104
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,560
Your Highness?

105
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:29,600
Why did you become a common spiritual fox?

106
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:33,920
How about your magic arts?

107
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,160
Did you lose them?

108
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:51,280
I'm pregnant with His Majesty's baby.

109
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,400
What has happened?

110
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,960
You're fooled, Your Highness.

111
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,680
If you got pregnant

112
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,320
from just kissing him,

113
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,920
I'd give birth to two sons.

114
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,360
Come on.

115
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,880
Now that you're here, just stay.

116
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,320
Write down

117
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,600
everything about how you become

118
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,680
what you are.

119
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,240
Write it down.

120
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,360
Dad.

121
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:08,280
Your Majesty, thank you for saving me.

122
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,880
The poison hasn't been removed completely.

123
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,920
You still need a good rest.

124
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,640
Min Su.

125
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,840
Your Majesty, how is Min Su doing?

126
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,040
He'll survive.

127
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:28,760
Your Majesty,

128
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,600
can I beg you for something?

129
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,040
My elder brother

130
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:35,880
Xu Yang

131
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:38,160
wouldn't spare Min Su.

132
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,200
Your Majesty,

133
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,400
can you help us?

134
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:46,680
The two of you...

135
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,400
We've known each other since childhood.

136
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,440
When I was young,

137
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,360
my brother wouldn't let me talk to anyone else.

138
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,120
Only Min Su stayed with me

139
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,800
and took care of me.

140
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:04,000
I don't want to marry the guy chosen by my brother.

141
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,840
But he...

142
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,000
Your Majesty,

143
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:14,800
I'll marry nobody

144
00:13:15,520 --> 00:13:16,920
but Min Su.

145
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:20,760
I hope you can help me.

146
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,120
Your Majesty, you've underestimated me.

147
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,280
How could you trap me in such a small ward?

148
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:45,840
Demon Lord,

149
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:46,760
Her Highness is back.

150
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:48,240
Where is she?

151
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,240
Just outside the palace.

152
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,360
She's with Emperor Dong Hua.

153
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,200
Dong Hua?

154
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:12,800
Dong Hua,

155
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,240
why is my sister injured?

156
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,360
She's poisoned with Qiushui Cold Toxin.

157
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,840
Qiushui?

158
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,440
Dong Hua,

159
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:24,920
you saved her life.

160
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,440
We're deeply grateful.

161
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:34,200
The poison hasn't been removed completely.

162
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:36,080
She still needs a good rest.

163
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,960
Thank you for your advice.

164
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:47,720
Dong Hua,

165
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,000
can you tell me

166
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:54,080
what on earth has happened between
you and Heng on Baishui Mountain?

167
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:55,720
Nothing special.

168
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:56,920
I just met her by chance.

169
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,120
By chance?

170
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:03,080
Dong Hua, do you still remember

171
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:06,240
what you promised us at the Forbidden Land?

172
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:07,600
Go ahead.

173
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:10,040
I hope

174
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:13,440
you can marry Ji Heng.

175
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,640
I'm afraid I can't.

176
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,480
You made a promise.

177
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:21,840
Do you want to go back on it?

178
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,640
It has nothing to do with my promise.

179
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,720
It's just I've never planned

180
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,800
to get married.

181
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:30,000
You once promised

182
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,640
you'd say yes to my request

183
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,120
as long as it's not morally wrong

184
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,360
and it doesn't hurt anyone.

185
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:37,000
Why are you making excuses?

186
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:41,760
So what?

187
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,360
Dong Hua,

188
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,800
your marriage matters a lot.

189
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:50,320
It's not something just between you and me.

190
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:54,200
I actually put it forward for the sake of the gods, the demons

191
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:56,680
and even the whole world.

192
00:15:57,920 --> 00:16:00,720
The gods and the demons will live together in peace

193
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:01,960
and there won't be wars anymore.

194
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,440
Isn't lasting peace

195
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,480
what you wish for?

196
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,000
So, you want your sister to marry me

197
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:19,720
for lasting peace of the six worlds.

198
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,240
Exactly.

199
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:24,560
What else do you think?

200
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,000
In this case,

201
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:27,280
you can send Ji Heng

202
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:30,760
to Tai Chen Palace in three months.

203
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,520
You agreed?

204
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,560
You have lofty ideals,

205
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,000
but you should also remember

206
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,320
Ji Heng will be one of the gods

207
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:40,480
after she marries into our clan

208
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:42,160
and then won't have to follow the rules of the demons.

209
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,120
Besides,

210
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:48,000
in case anything happens to your clan in the future,

211
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:52,120
I'm sure you'll keep sparing no effort

212
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:54,600
for the peace of the universe

213
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,840
and won't leave your clan members acting against the law.

214
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,320
For this purpose,

215
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:03,160
I have to fulfill your wish.

216
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,400
You have a great deal of foresight.

217
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,600
I admire you.

218
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:16,160
I've said yes to your request.

219
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,830
As for Ji Heng's guard,

220
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,110
how about forgiving him?

221
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:23,160
Now that she's going to marry you,

222
00:17:23,830 --> 00:17:25,350
I'll spare him.

223
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,560
His Majesty often makes an inspection tour like this.

224
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,240
It's not been a long time since he left.

225
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,640
Why do you miss him so much?

226
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,840
I'm really worried about you.

227
00:17:55,660 --> 00:17:58,600
His Majesty couldn't stay with you every day.

228
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,720
Well. Don't cry.

229
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,560
His Majesty asked me to take good care of you.

230
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:10,600
How about this?

231
00:18:11,130 --> 00:18:12,320
I'll open the ward

232
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,960
so that you can play around in the palace.

233
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,720
Okay?

234
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,080
Little fox, how can you lie to me?

235
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:29,720
I want to stay with His Majesty every now and then.

236
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,200
I'm going to meet him!

237
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:55,080
You little fox.

238
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,160
You deceived him into opening the ward.

239
00:18:59,810 --> 00:19:00,380
Your Majesty.

240
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:01,920
Foster brother, you're back.

241
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:04,440
Your Majesty.

242
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:06,610
Your Majesty,

243
00:19:06,610 --> 00:19:08,040
it turns out the little fox went to meet you.

244
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,840
Aren't they resin of cinnamomum camphora

245
00:19:27,840 --> 00:19:28,640
and stamens of green lotuses from Baishui Mountain?

246
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,120
It turns out he went to collect medicine for me.

247
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:33,880
These are the two kinds of effective medicine

248
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,920
to cure wounds, right?

249
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,440
Get the gallipot here.

250
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:06,880
His hand is injured.

251
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:08,600
It must've happened

252
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,120
when he got medicine for me.

253
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:13,080
I'll also make

254
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,440
a great healing ointment for him.

255
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:17,000
Jiu from the Imperial Kitchen is good at cooking.

256
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,760
Ask her to prepare food for the fox.

257
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:22,040
There is one thing I have to report to you.

258
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,800
Jiu disappeared.

259
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:26,480
I think she has something to do with the demon

260
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,720
who came here disguised as you.

261
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,840
You liar.

262
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,280
I'm open and aboveboard.

263
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,520
How could I be a spy of the demons?

264
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:36,080
I'm from Qingqiu.

265
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:37,880
You framed me up

266
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:40,160
just to stop me from coming back again.

267
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:42,160
Now that you care about the fox,

268
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:44,680
how about letting my subordinate Yu Ru take care of it?

269
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,600
It's better to leave me alone.

270
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:49,600
I may live a longer life

271
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,520
without your subordinate.

272
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:52,680
Don't bother.

273
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,640
Now that there is no suitable person,

274
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:56,680
I'll take care of it myself.

275
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:57,840
Foster brother,

276
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,560
we know nothing about the little fox's background.

277
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:02,040
I'm afraid it is transformed by some demon with magic arts.

278
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,560
You have to be careful.

279
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:04,800
You're thinking too much.

280
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:37,040
You can even cry.

281
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,760
Why can't you jump on me?

282
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:02,200
He sent me a piece of jade.

283
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:05,720
Is it the so-called token of affection?

284
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,520
You're so lively.

285
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,800
I'm sorry that you got trapped in the soul-locking jade

286
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:14,640
and almost lost your life.

287
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:17,280
It's nothing.

288
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:19,280
I'm willing to do anything

289
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,920
as long as I can stay by your side.

290
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:33,320
He used to be one of my generals.

291
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,080
He was bold and powerful at that time

