00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:40,080
and got me out of trouble several times.

293
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:41,320
Today,

294
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,760
I could do nothing but watch him die.

295
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:49,920
OMG.

296
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,040
I thought

297
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:55,720
he's the most resolute and ruthless god
in the Four Seas and Eight Deserts,

298
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:58,240
but he also feels sad sometimes.

299
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:03,920
What's so special

300
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,840
about love?

301
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:09,800
Why did a brave general like him choose to do that?

302
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,680
He could've survived.

303
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:16,240
Your Majesty,

304
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:18,320
I'm willing to do anything for you,

305
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:19,680
but,

306
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:22,120
I don't want to die for you.

307
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,880
It's not that I'm not sincere enough,

308
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:26,000
It's just

309
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:28,600
I prefer to live with you.

310
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,720
I have a great yearning to stay with you,

311
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:32,160
so I can't die.

312
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:33,960
I hate to part with you.

313
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:04,640
Your Highness,

314
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,480
you made trouble again.

315
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,560
Do you know your fur is...

316
00:24:12,840 --> 00:24:13,600
Did you draw it?

317
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:19,480
Flowers bloom and fade and turn into mud.

318
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:23,520
Safe and peaceful, we stay with each other forever.

319
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:25,040
Si Ming, you're impolite.

320
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,880
How can read my poem without my permission?

321
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:30,520
Just so so. It's a tongue twister at most.

322
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:31,720
You bad guy.

323
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:34,400
But I think

324
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,480
this painting is not bad.

325
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,800
Speaking of Technique of the Buddha's Seal Wheel,

326
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:42,240
only three people have grasped it.

327
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:46,600
The first is Mo Yuan from the Kunlun Mountain.

328
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,640
The second is the Buddha from Sukhavati.

329
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:53,600
The third is His Majesty.

330
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,000
You're most fortunate

331
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,800
to have a chance to see it.

332
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:57,920
That's for sure.

333
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,840
His Majesty is so powerful.

334
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,600
I'm bound to spread it

335
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:02,640
and let more people

336
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:04,200
know about the heroic epic.

337
00:25:06,560 --> 00:25:08,160
Si Ming, where is that thing?

338
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,400
This is what you want.

339
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:18,800
Don't open it completely.

340
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,880
Take out as much as you need.

341
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:39,640
What is it?

342
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,120
Cotton rose ointment.

343
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:03,800
Did you make it?

344
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,520
Wait a second.

345
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,040
Here you are.

346
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:35,560
♪ Falling flowers have a soft voice. ♪

347
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:39,040
♪ The wind talks to the Bodhi tree. ♪

348
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:46,440
♪ Bright-eyed, she's giving a little smile. ♪

349
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,040
Not bad.

350
00:26:47,560 --> 00:26:54,480
♪ When it comes to destiny, she couldn't help missing him. ♪

351
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:57,080
Good girl.

352
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:09,840
♪ Acacia sees time flying and the yearning between lovers. ♪

353
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:17,080
♪ She gets lovesick when failing to see him. ♪

354
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:24,800
♪ Life is like a wordless book. ♪

355
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:28,400
♪ The words uttered in her sleep are penetrating. ♪

356
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:34,840
♪ What scares me most is to realize it by myself. ♪

357
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:50,880
♪ The pain of separation makes my eyes blurred. ♪

358
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:54,760
♪ Looking carefully, I find it's Foling flowers. ♪

359
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:56,600
Is His Majesty

360
00:27:57,560 --> 00:28:00,200
painting with the brush I made for him?

361
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:02,520
That's to say,

362
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:05,520
I've got many memories about him without noticing.

363
00:28:06,320 --> 00:28:09,800
♪ Lovesickness is infinite. ♪

364
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:16,440
♪ What makes it keep raining? ♪

365
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:24,520
♪ Acacia sees time flying and the yearning between lovers. ♪

366
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:26,760
The mortals usually paint red the first petal

367
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:29,040
on the "double nine" diagrams

368
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,120
on the Winter Solstice.

369
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:33,080
By then,

370
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:35,840
I'll get your paws red

371
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,040
and paint with them.

372
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:38,520
What do you think?

373
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:40,920
His Majesty is also thinking about the future.

374
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:43,640
We'll spend a lot of time with each other in the future.

375
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:50,000
Alright.

376
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,400
From now on,

377
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,200
I'll stop eating my head off.

378
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:55,200
I'll be a useful fox

379
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:57,000
to bring glory to him.

380
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:09,840
♪ They remember each other no matter how the world is changing. ♪

381
00:29:09,940 --> 00:29:17,320
♪ I'll never give up unless the earth and heaven get old. ♪

382
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:24,400
♪ I hope destiny will bring us together. ♪

383
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:28,280
♪ It's melancholy and sorrowful. ♪

384
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:34,600
♪ It's miserable to part with who you love. ♪

385
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,960
I'll be a useful fox.

386
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:42,800
Well. I'll try to do that when summer is over.

387
00:30:06,320 --> 00:30:08,080
You really love the little fox.

388
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,280
To let it enjoy the shade,

389
00:30:09,440 --> 00:30:10,600
you've got two sandalwood trees cut

390
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,120
and rock crystal has been used to avoid water.

391
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,240
In this way

392
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:15,360
can it relax in the cool pavilion in midsummer.

393
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:22,000
I'm even inferior to a fox.

394
00:30:23,120 --> 00:30:24,280
Your Highness, please don't say that.

395
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,880
It's just a pet.

396
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,320
I've done so many things

397
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:31,600
for the sake of him.

398
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,280
But in the end,

399
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,480
it's a pet that has benefited from this.

400
00:30:54,760 --> 00:30:55,400
Your Majesty,

401
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:58,400
have you always been reading Buddhist scriptures alone

402
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,800
in the daytime

403
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:03,440
and at night?

404
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:15,800
As long as I'm here,

405
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:17,600
he won't feel lonely again.

406
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,560
I'll give all best things in the world

407
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,720
to him.

408
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:23,280
When I'm able to speak,

409
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:26,000
I'll deceive him into going to Qingqiu.

410
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,760
By then, I'll say this to him.

411
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:29,640
Look.

412
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,400
Stars here are so big.

413
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:32,420
They're not cute.

414
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:34,940
I can take you to Qingqiu

415
00:31:34,940 --> 00:31:35,700
and watch stars there.

416
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:36,800
Okay.

417
00:32:03,120 --> 00:32:04,880
Has His Majesty seen you

418
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:07,320
behave like this?

419
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:13,920
You won't listen to me unless I mention His Majesty.

420
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:22,360
Are you angry?

421
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:24,840
How about shaking hands?

422
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,640
Anger makes you age more quickly.

423
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:35,000
Look. I'm old enough.

424
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:36,840
I can't remember anything.

425
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,720
I can't remember who said

426
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:42,480
the root of Hanshi grass

427
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,160
is effective in helping people forget sorrow

428
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:46,880
and its flowers are top seasoning.

429
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:50,600
And I can't remember who wants the seed.

430
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:57,760
It's you.

431
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:05,200
I looked for it on purpose

432
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:07,200
when I went to Sukhavati for the Buddha's lectures.

433
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,420
It's said it's the last seed on Ling Mountain

434
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:11,160
in the Four Seas and Eight Deserts.

435
00:33:11,320 --> 00:33:12,480
The last one.

436
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:15,680
You're happy now.

437
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,560
I'll give it to you

438
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,400
when you leave the Sky Kingdom.

439
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:21,840
Your scared me.

440
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,640
Don't eat it!

441
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:41,400
I'll bury it here.

442
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:44,560
The location won't matter

443
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,240
if I can stay with His Majesty in the future.

444
00:34:00,120 --> 00:34:00,920
It's just cooked.

445
00:34:03,320 --> 00:34:03,960
By me.

446
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:05,600
Your Majesty.

447
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:08,840
I've been thinking about it.

448
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,880
His Majesty and I don't share the same hobbies.

449
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,120
I'm not good at anything he can do.

450
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,080
But unexpectedly,

451
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:16,280
he's also good at cooking, the only thing I'm expert at.

452
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,600
I finally found something

453
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,670
we're both good at.

454
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:28,190
I'm much relieved.

455
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:43,760
Is it good?

456
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:45,440
For real,

457
00:34:47,670 --> 00:34:49,280
it's so...

458
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:52,230
...so awful.

459
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:58,280
What should be the look on my face when I talk to him?

460
00:34:59,120 --> 00:35:00,400
My auntie once told me

461
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:02,670
a story about a bride.

462
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,360
She was not good at cooking.

463
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:06,800
One day, she was seized by a whim

464
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,040
and decided to cook soup.

465
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:11,040
She won high praise from her husband.

466
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:14,800
Later, the bride tasted the soup

467
00:35:14,960 --> 00:35:16,640
when she did the dishes,

468
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,320
only to find

469
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,800
her husband said those words

470
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:22,520
to make her happy.

471
00:35:23,120 --> 00:35:24,040
So...

472
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:29,280
Then the couple loved each other more.

473
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,160
It became an interesting story

474
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:33,200
on everybody's lips.

475
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:36,320
I can't tell him it's awful.

476
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,600
Your Majesty,

477
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:05,920
please observe carefully

478
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:09,000
and realize I'm smiling with a little reluctance.

479
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,120
It'd be best

480
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:13,120
if you taste it yourself.

481
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:18,600
Do you mean...

482
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:24,400
You want to have some more?

483
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,200
There is no more for today.

484
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:29,080
I'll cook for you tomorrow.

485
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:34,320
Don't bother.

486
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,480
I've tasted it.

487
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:38,920
It's awful.

488
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:40,680
But I think

489
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:43,040
it may be to your taste now that you're a different species.

490
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:45,040
So I took it to you.

491
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:46,440
As expected,

492
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,040
you foxes really have a different taste.

493
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:53,280
I've eaten so much food prepared by His Majesty

494
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:55,040
that I've lost lots of fur.

495
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,720
If it goes on like this,

496
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,360
I'd become bald.

497
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:04,200
It seems I have no other choice

498
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,880
but to tell him the truth.

499
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:09,760
Alright.

500
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,040
I'll use body language to tell him

501
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:15,040
I don't like the carp.

502
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:17,840
Good tea.

503
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,000
There is a guest.

504
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,520
I can't eavesdrop on them.

505
00:38:22,040 --> 00:38:23,040
It's impolite.

506
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:25,720
Your Majesty,

507
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,800
I haven't heard that

508
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,120
you're interested in pets.

509
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:30,880
Why did you suddenly raise a spiritual fox?

510
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,000
It's special.

511
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:34,680
Maybe it's destiny.

512
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,280
Don't try to fool me.

513
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,760
I've seen spiritual foxes

514
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,800
better-looking than that.

515
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,960
The ladies in the Bai family of Qingqiu

516
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,760
are all gorgeous.

517
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,440
What's special

518
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:47,880
about your fox?

519
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,760
It likes the sweet and sour fish

520
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:53,240
made by me.

521
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,080
It's really special.

522
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,800
Such being the case,

523
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:11,000
if I tell him

524
00:39:11,080 --> 00:39:12,440
I was lying,

525
00:39:12,560 --> 00:39:12,960
then...

526
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:15,440
Anyway,

527
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:17,400
it's a white lie.

528
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:19,960
I'd better just let it continue.

529
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:23,320
If I keep eating the fish cooked by him,

530
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:25,880
all my fur would fall out,

531
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:28,160
but it doesn't matter.

532
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,240
I'll pretend

533
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,640
it's time to molt.

534
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,920
Did you just smile?

535
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:07,040
Do you like it?

536
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:10,320
Yes.

537
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:29,280
Have a look. Do you like it?

538
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,440
I like all your paintings.

539
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,760
Wait for me at the central yard if you wake up.

540
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,600
I'll feed you.

541
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,800
What's special about that little fox?

542
00:40:55,680 --> 00:40:56,680
It's more important than me in your mind.

543
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:58,520
Why?

544
00:40:59,120 --> 00:40:59,680
Anyway,

545
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,600
in this case, I can't go to the west desert

546
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,960
to do what you want me to.

547
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:06,040
I promised your father I'd look after you.

548
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,600
I mean what I say.

549
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:10,040
It's just a pet. Don't take it seriously.

550
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,360
See?

551
00:41:33,080 --> 00:41:34,120
In his mind,

552
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,760
you're just a pet.

553
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,040
But you always dream of staying with him.

554
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:40,000
Don't you think it's ridiculous?

555
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,640
Now I can go to the west desert and give rain.

556
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,760
I wonder if he's still interested in you

557
00:41:47,480 --> 00:41:49,480
when I come back.

558
00:41:50,720 --> 00:41:53,680
I hope I can still see you in Tai Chen Palace.

559
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,600
His Majesty is so nice to me.

560
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:29,120
Am I really just a pet in his mind?

561
00:42:30,720 --> 00:42:32,240
If he knows my true identity...

562
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,880
If I tell him

563
00:42:35,000 --> 00:42:36,080
I'm Princess of Qingqiu,

564
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,560
will he blame me?

565
00:42:40,320 --> 00:42:41,760
He drew paintings with me

566
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:44,480
and sent me such nice white jade.

567
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:46,720
He said so much to me with me in his arms.

568
00:43:30,480 --> 00:43:31,320
Little thing,

569
00:43:31,800 --> 00:43:33,800
you're so naughty,

570
00:43:34,040 --> 00:43:35,760
but His Majesty just won't get mad at you.

571
00:43:36,960 --> 00:43:39,440
That's because I'm important in his mind.

572
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:48,200
Go with me.

573
00:43:48,520 --> 00:43:49,600
